parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake pedal can cause extended stopping distances, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal goes to the floor
the vehicle takes longer to stop
the ABS brakes do not function properly
the wheels lock up
and the vehicle experiences premature wear of brake pads.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS brakes can cause the wheels to lock up, leading to loss of control and accidents.
symptoms: The ABS brakes do not function properly
the wheels lock up
the vehicle experiences extended stopping distances
and the brake pedal feels soft or spongy.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Premature Wear of Brake Pads and Rotors
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The premature wear of brake pads and rotors can cause the brakes to fail, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The brake pads and rotors wear out prematurely
the brakes make a loud popping sound
and the vehicle experiences vibration and shimmies.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake hydraulic system can cause the brakes to fail, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal goes to the floor
and the vehicle experiences extended stopping distances.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the side cargo door hinges can cause the doors to become inoperable, trapping passengers inside, and creating a safety hazard.
symptoms: Stiff or difficult-to-open doors
broken or cracked hinges
rusted or frozen hinges
doors barely open or close
sheet metal flexing as the door tries to open and close.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The blind spot to the right of intersections can cause accidents or near-misses, potentially leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Reduced visibility to the right of intersections
difficulty seeing other vehicles or pedestrians.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden tire tread separation or failure can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Loud noise or explosion-like sound
tire blowout
tread peeling off
sidewalls coming off
loss of vehicle control
unusual vibrations or sounds while driving.
